FBIS3-47100 "dreas006_h_94003" FBIS-EAS-94-006 Document Type:Daily Report 10 Jan 1994 Brunei, Malaysia & Singapore Malaysia Mahathir Appoints New Deputy Finance Minister BK0801083694 Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia in English 0800 GMT 8 Jan 94 BK0801083694 Kuala Lumpur Voice of Malaysia Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Senator Mustapha Mohamed has been appointed Deputy Finance Minister to replace Datuk Abdul Ghani Othman, who is now the Youth and Sports Minister. At the same time, Datuk Dr Ali Abu Sudin Omar has been appointed the parliamentary secretary to the Finance Ministry replacing Senator Mustapha. Prime Minister Datuk Sri Dr Mahathir Mohamed announced this today.
